data.description: Affordable Nice Ranch in a Desirable Neighborhood?! Located in a Swim/Playground/Tennis community, far enough away from the city, but a short drive to Downtown Conyers. A short commute ride that can be driven highway or back streets to Downtown Atlanta. This Three Bedroom, Two Bathroom Ranch home has been well maintained by its owners. You will love the beautiful details including a kitchen with white cabinetry and granite counters, stainless steel appliances and a gas stove.  This home has a large separate owners suite opposite end away from the other rooms with trey ceilings, a bath with separate shower and an amazing sized soaking tub! Cozy up in your living room complete with a fireplace and vaulted ceilings! This winter you can eat smores outside over a warm firepit or share warm Cider in the screened-in porch located off the kitchen plus an additional patio. Come and fall in love with the close to half an acre of your own park-like grounds with a large front yard and plenty of space between your neighbors! Schools, Grocery Stores, Hardware, Target and many Local Eateries are all within minutes. Go and show today!
